@startuml SDA-Pro_Sequence_Ingestion
!theme plain
autonumber
title Sequence: Alert Ingestion → Enrichment → Incident Creation\n(Composite, Factory Method, Chain of Responsibility, State, Observer)
actor "Splunk SIEM" as Splunk
participant "AlertIngestionService" as AIS
participant "AlertNormalizerFactory\n(Factory Method)" as Fact
participant "SplunkNormalizer" as Norm
participant "AlertCampaign\n(Composite)" as Campaign
participant "SingleAlert" as Alert
participant "EnrichmentPipeline\n(CoR Assembler)" as Pipe
participant "DeduplicationHandler\n(CoR: H1)" as H1
participant "GeoIPHandler\n(CoR: H2)" as H2
participant "ThreatIntelHandler\n(CoR: H3)" as H3
participant "ClassificationHandler\n(CoR: H4)" as H4
participant "ThreatIntelProxy\n(Proxy)" as Proxy
participant "VirusTotalAdapter\n(Adapter)" as VTAd
participant "EnrichmentService" as ECS
participant "CorrelationStrategy\n(Strategy)" as Strat
participant "IncidentManagementService" as IMS
participant "NewState\n(State)" as NewSt
participant "Incident" as Incident
participant "EventBusPublisher\n(Singleton + Observer)" as EB
participant "DashboardUpdater\n(Observer)" as DashObs
participant "AuditLogger\n(Observer)" as AuditObs
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
== 1. Alert Ingestion ==
Splunk -> AIS : POST /ingest/splunk (webhook)
AIS -> AIS : validateSourceAuth()
== 2. Factory Method — Normalize ==
AIS -> Fact : createNormalizer(SPLUNK)
Fact -> Norm : new SplunkNormalizer()
Fact --> AIS : normalizer
AIS -> Norm : normalize(rawPayload)
Norm -> Norm : mapSplunkSchemaToCanonical()
Norm --> AIS : CanonicalAlert
== 3. Composite — Group into Campaign ==
AIS -> Campaign : new AlertCampaign("APT29-Campaign")
AIS -> Campaign : add(alert)
Campaign -> Alert : new SingleAlert(canonicalData)
Campaign --> AIS : compositeAlert
== 4. Chain of Responsibility — Enrichment Pipeline ==
AIS -> Pipe : assemblePipeline()
Pipe -> H1 : setNext(H2)
H1 -> H2 : setNext(H3)
H2 -> H3 : setNext(H4)
AIS -> H1 : handle(campaign)
H1 -> H1 : checkDuplicate(campaign)
H1 -> H1 : not duplicate
H1 -> H2 : doHandle(campaign)
H2 -> H2 : enrichGeoIP(campaign)
H2 -> H2 : addLocationContext()
H2 -> H3 : doHandle(campaign)
H3 -> Proxy : checkReputation(ip, IP_ADDRESS)
Proxy -> Proxy : checkCache()
alt Cache miss
Proxy -> VTAd : queryVirusTotal(ip)
VTAd -> VTAd : mapToCanonicalFormat()
VTAd --> Proxy : reputationScore
Proxy -> Proxy : cacheResult()
else Cache hit
Proxy --> H3 : cachedReputation
end
Proxy --> H3 : ReputationResult.MALICIOUS
H3 -> H3 : addThreatContext()
H3 -> H4 : doHandle(campaign)
H4 -> H4 : classifySeverity(campaign)
H4 -> H4 : severity = CRITICAL
H4 --> Pipe : EnrichmentResult.COMPLETE
== 5. Strategy — Correlation ==
Pipe --> AIS : enrichedCampaign
AIS -> ECS : processEnrichedAlert(campaign)
ECS -> Strat : correlate(enrichedCampaign)
Strat -> Strat : patternMatch("lateral-movement")
Strat -> Strat : exceedsThreshold(3, CRITICAL)
Strat --> ECS : CorrelationResult.CREATE_INCIDENT
== 6. State — Incident Creation ==
ECS -> IMS : createIncident(campaign, correlationResult)
IMS -> Incident : new Incident(campaign)
Incident -> Incident : setState(NewState)
NewSt -> NewSt : onEnter(incident)
NewSt -> NewSt : scheduleAutoTriage(incident, 5min)
Incident --> IMS : incident
IMS -> DB : INSERT incident
== 7. Observer — Event Publication ==
IMS -> EB : publishIncidentCreated(incident)
EB -> MQ : push "IncidentCreated" event
par Parallel Observer Reactions
MQ -> DashObs : consume event
DashObs -> DashObs : updateIncidentQueue()
DashObs --> Analyst : WebSocket push (new incident)
end
MQ -> AuditObs : consume event
AuditObs -> AuditObs : logIncidentCreation()
AuditObs -> DB : INSERT audit trail
== 8. Response ==
IMS --> ECS : incidentId
ECS --> AIS : success
AIS --> Splunk : 202 Accepted
@enduml
